{
  "stem": "21550.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a Polish detective took us into a courtyard and said, I want some money from you, for no reason at all.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had no rights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to give him whatever we had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we fought back on different fronts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mentioned my sister Lilka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was enrolled in a school, where the Germans forbade all kinds of schooling.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no schooling at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we tried to find-- to fight  back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We organized illegal schools in apartments.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they organized a library system, whereby people exchanged books without going to a library, because the libraries were closed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got underground newspapers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were people who had little-- what do you call those presses, by hand, and they distributed it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything-- every-- every activity was illegal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no legal activity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were-- there were people-- despite the fact that the-- the borderline was always watched over by the Germans, people would smuggle out of the ghetto, get news, get information, and bring it back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how we found out in 1942 when they-- when they started this-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the action to bring the people out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the Final Solution.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were trying to get the people not to resist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first few days, a lot of people believed them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then after a few days, word came back that there's no work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's no [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] any place built there to-- to-- to get to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it's they're going directly to the death camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
